  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Speedboat Simulator!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/99268de9765fa59406d8e9437c994947.avif?t=1772360610\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedboat Simulator is a realistic speedboat racing game where you pilot high-speed boats, customize their colors, and compete in thrilling races. Navigate through Hawaiian waters, and make a splash when you reach the finish line!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Speedboat Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedboat Simulator is a thrilling speedboat racing experience that combines realistic simulation with high-octane action. Get behind the wheel of powerful speedboats, each with unique handling and acceleration, and test your skills on various challenging tracks. Customize your boats with different colors and take on opponents in intense races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features multiple game modes, including singleplayer and spectator mode, allowing players to either compete or watch the action unfold. With responsive controls, dynamic water physics, and adrenaline-pumping speeds, every race is a battle against the clock and the competition. As the game evolves, expect more boats, tracks, and customization options, providing endless ways to enjoy the ultimate speedboat racing experience!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedboat Simulator is a realistic speedboat racing game where you pilot high-speed boats, customize their colors, and compete in thrilling races. Navigate through Hawaiian waters, and make a splash when you reach the finish line!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Speedboat Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedboat Simulator is a thrilling speedboat racing experience that combines realistic simulation with high-octane action. Get behind the wheel of powerful speedboats, each with unique handling and acceleration, and test your skills on various challenging tracks. Customize your boats with different colors and take on opponents in intense races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features multiple game modes, including singleplayer and spectator mode, allowing players to either compete or watch the action unfold. With responsive controls, dynamic water physics, and adrenaline-pumping speeds, every race is a battle against the clock and the competition. As the game evolves, expect more boats, tracks, and customization options, providing endless ways to enjoy the ultimate speedboat racing experience!</p>",
